OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,FAn allergy sufferer said she feared
OL,8,Ffor her life after vital medication
OL,9,Fwas taken from her during a night out.
OL,11,FLauryn Forrester's emergency EpiPen
OL,12,Finjector was confiscated twice at the
OL,13,FElectrowerkz nightclub in Islington.
OL,15,FThe device works quickly to counter
OL,16,Flife-threatening symptoms, including
OL,17,Fthose caused by Lauryn's allergy to
OL,18,Fcertain types of nuts.
OL,20,F"It's my lifeline," Lauryn said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
