OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781783276
OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,F"I didn't want to hand it over. I was
OL,8,Fvery anxious and very wary.
OL,10,F"I was scared because it wasn't in my
OL,11,Fline of sight. They could put it down
OL,12,Fand forget where they had put it, and
OL,13,Fthen if I needed it, it wouldn't be
OL,14,Fthere.
OL,16,F"There can't be any delay. If I need
OL,17,Fit, I need it immediately.
OL,19,F"If I didn't have it and I went into
OL,20,Fanaphylactic shock, it would be
OL,21,Fdevastating."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
