CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781783276
OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,FEpiPens are at risk of being
OL,8,Fconfiscated because they can be used
OL,9,Fto smuggle drugs into bars and clubs.
OL,11,FLauryn added: "I understand the
OL,12,Fbouncer was just doing her job, but
OL,13,Fpeople without allergies are less
OL,14,Flikely to understand.
OL,16,F"If I was a bouncer at this club, I
OL,17,Fwouldn't accept this policy. There's
OL,18,Fno reason anyone should have their
OL,19,Fmedication taken from them."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
