OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,FElectrowerkz is a large nightclub
OL,8,Fspanning five levels and covering more
OL,9,Fthan 30,000 square feet, meaning
OL,10,Fconfiscated EpiPens could be stored a
OL,11,Fconsiderable distance from their
OL,12,Fowners.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
