OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781783276
OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,FThe club said it had carried out a
OL,8,F"full review of this policy" with
OL,9,F"specialist legal advice", adding:
OL,10,F"Guest safety, particularly around
OL,11,Fmedical needs, is something we take
OL,12,Fvery seriously, and we're sorry to
OL,13,Fhear that this guest felt anxious
OL,14,Fabout access to her medication on the
OL,15,Fnights in question.
OL,17,F"Her experience matters to us, and
OL,18,Fit's exactly the kind of feedback that
OL,19,Fhas prompted us to look closely at
OL,20,Fthis policy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
