OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,F"Our revised policy now allows
OL,8,Fcustomers to choose whether their
OL,9,Fmedication is stored securely with our
OL,10,Fmedical team and made available
OL,11,Fwhenever requested, or kept with them.
OL,13,F"If kept with them, a confidential and
OL,14,Fdiscreet log detailing the medication
OL,15,Ftype, customer name and date is
OL,16,Fsecurely stored, with access limited
OL,17,Fto senior management only, and
OL,18,Fsecurely destroyed after a set
OL,19,Fretention period.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
