CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781783276
OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,F"We presented this revised policy to
OL,8,Fthe authorities, who were satisfied
OL,9,Ffor it to be implemented.
OL,11,F"The new policy is clearly set out on
OL,12,Four website."
OL,14,FThe Security Industry Authority said
OL,15,Feffective search procedures included
OL,16,Funderstanding people with "diverse
OL,17,Fneeds such as medical requirements".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
