OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,FExperts say every minute counts when
OL,8,Ftreating anaphylaxis, which is
OL,9,Fapproached by emergency services with
OL,10,Fthe same urgency as a cardiac arrest.
OL,12,FLauryn Forrester lives every day not
OL,13,Fknowing when her next reaction may
OL,14,Fhappen. Even touching her face or
OL,15,Fmouth can trigger a reaction.
OL,17,F"The person serving my drink could
OL,18,Fhave eaten nuts on their break and
OL,19,Fthen handed me my drink," she said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
