CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781783276
OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,F"If that happens in a large venue with
OL,8,Fmultiple floors, how am I supposed to
OL,9,Fget to the medical room in time?
OL,11,F"Especially if I've been drinking. If
OL,12,FI'm suffering anaphylactic shock and
OL,13,FI'm two floors away, it could be too
OL,14,Flate."
OL,16,FA mother who understands the fatal
OL,17,Fdangers of allergic reactions is Tanya
OL,18,FEdnan-Laperouse. Her teenage daughter,
OL,19,FNatasha, died after eating a baguette
OL,20,Fcontaining unlabelled sesame seeds.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
