CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781783276
OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,F"Whenever someone has a reaction, they
OL,8,Fmust tell someone else what's
OL,9,Fhappening, and the chances of them
OL,10,Fbeing able to find the right person to
OL,11,Fhelp in a really crowded venue are
OL,12,Fslim," Tanya said.
OL,14,F"You can lose such precious moments.
OL,16,F"The most important thing is that they
OL,17,Fhave their medication with them, so
OL,18,Fthey, or somebody else, can administer
OL,19,Fan injection.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
