OL,3,CITV News London found door staff at
OL,4,Cclubs and bars insist items are handed
OL,5,Cover.
OL,7,F"This could help delay the onset of
OL,8,Fanaphylaxis.
OL,10,FWorld Allergy Week later this month
OL,11,Faims to raise awareness of symptoms
OL,12,Fand treatments, and to remind people
OL,13,Fhow unpredictable allergies can be.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
